# CNN ki Limitations — Easy Hinglish mein 😄

---

## 🔑 Main Point:
CNN **patterns aur minute details** pakad leta hai jo human eye miss kar deti hai — **BUT** image ka **actual meaning/context samajhna** uske bas ki baat nahi!

---

## ❌ Limitations:

### 1. 🚫 Content Samajhna Nahi Aata
- Social media pe **inappropriate content moderate** karne ke liye CNNs use hue
- Bahut saari images pe train kiya gaya tha
- **Phir bhi 100% inappropriate content block nahi kar paya**
- Kyunki wo **context nahi samajhta** — bas pattern dekhta hai

### 2. 💡 Lighting & Angle Change karo — CNN Confuse!
- Studies ne prove kiya ki **ImageNet** pe train kiya hua CNN...
- Same object ko **alag angle ya alag lighting** mein dekhe toh **detect nahi kar pata!**
- Human toh easily pehchaan leta — CNN nahi

### 3. 🧠 Human Intelligence Replicate Nahi Ho Sakti (Abhi Tak)
- CNN aaj **facial recognition, image search, AR, editing** mein use ho raha hai
- Achievements **remarkable hain** — but...
- **Human brain jaisi intelligence** abhi bhi bahut door hai

---

## 🎯 One Line Summary:
> CNN **dekhta bahut hai, samajhta kam hai** — pattern ka king hai, but common sense zero! 😂
